"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/101191","Ministry of Justice","false","2014-11-03","<p /> <p>The data requested on PFI projects is publically available via the following link:</p><p> </p><p><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/private-finance-initiative-projects-2013-summary-data." target="_blank">https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/private-finance-initiative-projects-2013-summary-data.</a></p><p> </p><p>The data accessed via this link can be filtered by procuring authority and then by date of financial close in order to determine how many PFI projects were contracted by a Department in a specific year.</p><p> </p><p>This information is provided by Departments and published by the Treasury each year. The current data is as at 31 March 2013 but will be updated with data as at 31 March 2014 shortly.</p>","Bermondsey and Old Southwark","Simon Hughes",,"2014-11-03T12:35:53.770359Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/101191/answer","Biography information for Simon Hughes","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/101191/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/101191/answer",,,,,"54","Justice","Justice","2014-10-27","Private Finance Initiative","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Justice, how many private finance initiative projects his Department contracted for in each year from 1997 to 2010.","false","Biography information for Simon Kirby","Brighton, Kemptown","Simon Kirby","212101"
