"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/100711","Department of Health","false","2014-10-28","<p>The attached table shows finished admission episodes with a primary diagnosis of asthma by age for the years 2008-09 to 2012-13.</p><p> </p>","North Norfolk","Norman Lamb",,"2014-10-28T15:20:28.1661387Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/100711/answer","Biography information for Norman Lamb","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/100711/answer","Finished admission episodes- Asthma-2008-09 to 2012-13.xlsx","Finished admission episodes- Asthma-2008-09 to 2012-13.xlsx","Asthma admissions- 2008-09 to 2012-13","Asthma admissions- 2008-09 to 2012-13","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/100711/answer",,,,,"17","Health","Health","2014-10-23","Asthma","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Health, how many finished hospital admission episodes with a primary diagnosis of asthma there were among people aged (a) under and (b) over 18 in each of the last five years.","false","Biography information for Liz Kendall","Leicester West","Liz Kendall","211702"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/100712","Department of Health","false","2014-10-28","<p>This information is not collected centrally.</p><p> </p><p><strong> </strong></p><p> </p><p>However, the following table shows the number of people recorded on a general practice register as part of the quality and outcomes framework (QOF), with a diagnosis of asthma for all ages for England. The data from the QOF are collected by general practice and not by geographical location and are not broken down by age.</p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><table><tbody><tr><td><p>2008-09</p></td><td><p>3,197,726</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>2009-10</p></td><td><p>3,254,562</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>2010-11</p></td><td><p>3,273,174</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>2011-12</p></td><td><p>3,295,944</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>2012-13</p></td><td><p>3,359,368</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p>","North Norfolk","Norman Lamb",,"2014-10-28T15:43:49.0338423Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/100712/answer","Biography information for Norman Lamb","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/100712/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/100712/answer",,,,,"17","Health","Health","2014-10-23","Asthma","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Health, how many people aged (a) under and (b) over 18 were diagnosed with asthma in each of the last five years.","false","Biography information for Liz Kendall","Leicester West","Liz Kendall","211703"
